	<h1 class="title">小区里遍布智能快递柜这件事，很可能永远不会发生</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1741/small/1741.jpg?1435203015" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">高宇馨 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-11 08:38:53 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/10648/medium/10648.jpg?1436646794" alt="" />			
	</div>
